            <img src= "/images/project1.jpg" alt="Project 1">
            <p>This project focuses on addressing various aspects of climate change through innovative and comprehensive solutions. Climate change is one of the most pressing global challenges, leading to rising temperatures, sea level rise, extreme weather events, and widespread ecological disruptions. This project works across multiple sectors including agriculture, waste management, energy efficiency, and environmental education to develop holistic strategies that can reduce greenhouse gas emissions and promote sustainable practices.</p>
            <a href="/solutions/projects/1"><button>View</button></a>
